~chatplayer("<p,quiz>Have there been many victims of the plague?");
~chatnpc("<p,sad>You could say that... I've heard reports that half of West Ardougne is infected! Many have lost friends and family...");
~chatplayer("<p,quiz>It sounds an awful way to live.");
~chatnpc("<p,sad>People are very depressed and scared. I've never met anyone fully infected though. I suppose we should be grateful to the mourners for that.");

[label,carla_i_hope_things_get_eaiser_for_you]
